showUserPublicProfile?gid=futumsh>Futumsh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/6/02 12:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1569.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Doomshade</span><hr size=1> He's straight melee with flurry, unslowable.  Keep agro on a tank and keep the tank alive and you're set.  His damage output is a bit less than Vindi, but spikey due to flurries. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xenojones>XENOJONES</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 533<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/6/02 1:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1569.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Doomshade</span><hr size=1> Doomshade will corpse camp unlike the other mobs in the zone. Pull him to the end of the tunnel and wait for the other mobs to leave then pull him solo.<br>
<br>
Use a DS potion, Mage DS and bard. Use defensive and gank him.<br>
<br>
ROllen's DPS with the triple DS while defensive 250<br>
Doomshade's DPS while Rollen was defensive 270<br>
<br>
One cleric while work, but have a second just in case. Not sure of your stats and I remember him when I was 60th and we needed three clerics. My AC is 1450 buffed and my HPs were about 8200 and 65th lvl.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
